---
/*
  /resources/automation-guide — practitioner guide to publishing automation.

  Section order:
    1. Hero (universal, with PublishingPipelineCard side panel — static)
    2. AnimatedDivider
    3. Framing prose + before/after outcome strip
    4. AnimatedDivider
