       folded into each stage's "Validates" line)
    6. AnimatedDivider
    7. Containerization (prose + Dockerfile code block + What's in the image)
    8. AnimatedDivider
    9. Output formats (typographic table + Gradle code block)
   10. AnimatedDivider
   11. CI/CD platforms (vertical entries + GitHub Actions code block)
   12. AnimatedDivider
   13. Custom DITA-OT plugins (vertical entries + maintenance principle)
   14. AnimatedDivider
